[normal]Are the public purposes in the current Charter the right ones? How might they change?[bold]8.
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]There should be a greater emphasis on encouraging 
[normal]UK
[normal] creativity and innovation, as well as greater diversity of content for 
[normal]L
[normal]icence Fee Payers
[normal], via ind
[normal]ependently produced content. 
[normal]What scope, scale and remit should the BBC have?[bold]Should the BBC’s output and services be provided to any greater or lesser degr[bold]ee for particular audiences?[bold]9.
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]The BBC should ensure that the nations of the 
[normal]UK
[normal] are having their stories told and lives reflected both in the
[normal]ir
