[normal]What balance should be struck in wh[bold]at the BBC produces in-house, commissions externally and leaves entirely to others to create?[bold]10.
[normal]&#xa0; 
[normal]Moving 
[normal] forward there will be an 
[normal]increasing 
[normal]need for the BBC to be flexible
[normal], whilst not allowing for 
[normal]itself to be outpaced by technological
[normal] advancements
[normal] and conve
[normal]rgence-related change. For this reason a BBC which is more slimline in structure, 
[normal]less bureaucratic and top heavy, 
[normal]with
[normal] a healthier balance between in-house and externally produced content
[normal] would make sense
[normal].  T
[normal]his will also allow it 
[normal]to 
