[normal]As part of the 2010 CSR, this arrangement was altered by the DCMS. The new arrangement meant that S4C had its budget reduced in real terms by some 36% - the main
[normal] part of its continuing funding was to come from the TV Licence Fee, with a remaining c£7m to be a continuing grant from DCMS. 
[normal]Its other 
