[normal]funding reductions for S4C of 1% in 2013-14 and 2% in 2014-15. Following the Chancellor’s Spring Budget Statement in 2013 further cuts were announced of 1.09% in 2013-14 and 1.06% in 2014-15.
[normal] Lastly, the BBC Trust then included S4C’s non-content costs with
